	.string "Warp panels, the Hideout's pride\n"
	.string "and joy!\p"
	.string "You're clueless about where you are,\n"
	.string "aren't you?\p"
	.string "Fluster and tire out the enemy, then\n"
	.string "lower the boom! That's our plan!$"

